transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Are you the client of Viagra? How can I help you today?

Speaker 2: Yes, sir. I'm calling to cancel my subscription. I no longer need it.

Speaker 1: Can I take a look into that for you? What's your last name and a zip code?

Speaker 2: Last name is Trest. T-R-E-S-T. Zip code is 33898.

Speaker 1: Okay. One quick thing I do want to mention, sir, now that I'm looking at your profile,

Speaker 2: is that you're currently a VIP member for the Viagra AGV.

Speaker 1: The moment I cancel these orders out, you wouldn't be able to access this Viagra anymore.

Speaker 2: Are you sure you didn't want to change it to our six-month freeze plan?

Speaker 1: No, I did that before. I no longer need them. I want to cancel them altogether.

Speaker 2: No problem. No worries at all. Just letting you know, because the moment it is canceled,

Speaker 1: the doctor would delete the prescription as well.

Speaker 2: Yeah, I'm going to do everything. Cancel everything. I don't want nothing else.

Speaker 1: Nothing else? Okay. It was already canceled out. So I hope you have a great day.

Speaker 2: All right, then. I appreciate it, bud.

Speaker 1: You're no problem. Bye-bye.
